	   <tr><td colspan=2>level 16-20 was hands down the lowest point of my Wizard career was lvl 16-20.&nbsp;&nbsp;I learned at 20 where I should be, and I wish I had gone there sooner! Lake Rathe!!!  There are 3 Bird camps, and several other things to fight. My favorite was the Arena camp:  once you zone in from South Karana, go straight into the zone (run up the wall to avoid the Gnolls, or fight them if they are still good xp) and swim out into the water.  Veer right till you find the Island with the Arena zone entrance. Fight the little birds here, and eventually move to the big ones when you can handle them.  This was one of the few places I could solo easily without Snare or SoW, and is still my favorite hunting spot in all of Norrath<br>A <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
