	   <tr><td colspan=2>The BEST way to play a wiz from ground up...From 1-9, solo...find a spot with blues near a safe place to med, root, burn, rinse, repeat...<br><br>At 10, the mob hp start going up, and you end up wasting too much time running for zones with the root routine.&nbsp;&nbsp;You need a friend.  Just one.  Go to a popular zone, like ECommons, and advertise for a partner, not a group.  2 of any class, when one is a wiz, can get exp 1.5 times faster both soloing.  Best possible is a shaman or druid, but I had great success from 11 to 20 with a monk buddy. EC from 10-12, wisps in WC from 12-13, then move to the Oasis at 14 for sick exp off of the caimen and crocs...<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
