	   <tr><td colspan=2>The secret to leveling a wizard is finding a good spot to solo. You might think you spend most of your time medding, but the xp goes much faster solo all the same, and medding is faster than healing any time. Kill low blues and high greens. Find a spot where you can med safely between fights, and can find as stuff to attack as fast as you med up. I would suggest gnolls in the Blackburrow area at your level (I think, it's been so long, you still can get xp there). Low to mid teens, Wisps (careful to only get one, they are very bad in multiples). Lavastorm after a bit higher, and Lake Rathe high teens to low 20's. Root and nuke, and as little melee as you can get away with. Once you are in your 20's, all your fights should be with magic.<br>&nbsp;<br>Daeanor Endarion<br>Sorceror of the Rathe</td></tr>
